Package: rapmod
Title: Shiny Application Modules for Registries at Rapporteket
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Are",
           family = "Edvardsen",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "biorakel@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5210-3656"))
Description: Provides shiny application modules for registries at Rapporteket
    <https://rapporteket.github.io/rapporteket/articles/short_introduction.html>.
    These modules represent common tools that are often required by registries
    using Rapporteket as a report service. The motivation and purpose of this
    pacakge is to improve user experience and reduce development and maintenance
    time across registries at Rapporteket.
